[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "The corrupt ways by which in this our time they arrive at the height to which their ambitions aspire, manifestly enough declares that their ends cannot be very good.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Let us tell ambition that it is she herself who gives us a taste of solitude; for what does she so much avoid as society?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "What does she so much seek as elbowroom?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "the contagion is very dangerous in the crowd.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "A man must either imitate the vicious or hate them both are dangerous things, either to resemble them because they are many or to hate many because they are unresembling to ourselves.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Merchants who go to sea are in the right when they are cautious that those who embark with them in the same bottom be neither dissolute blasphemers nor vicious other ways, looking upon such society as unfortunate.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000007_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000007_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "'tis not that a wise man may not live everywhere content, and be alone in the very crowd of a palace; but if it be left to his own choice, the schoolman will tell you that he should fly the very sight of the crowd: he will endure it if need be; but if it be referred to him, he will choose to be alone.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000007_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000007_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Charondas punished those as evil men who were convicted of keeping ill company.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000007_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000007_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "There is nothing so unsociable and sociable as man, the one by his vice, the other by his nature.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Now the end, I take it, is all one, to live at more leisure and at one's ease: but men do not always take the right way.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Moreover, for having shaken off the court and the exchange, we have not taken leave of the principal vexations of life:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "ambition, avarice, irresolution, fear, and inordinate desires, do not leave us because we forsake our native country:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "they often follow us even to cloisters and philosophical schools; nor deserts, nor caves, hair shirts, nor fasts, can disengage us from them:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "[\"Why do we seek climates warmed by another sun?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "If a man do not first discharge both himself and his mind of the burden with which he finds himself oppressed, motion will but make it press the harder and sit the heavier, as the lading of a ship is of less encumbrance when fast and bestowed in a settled posture.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "You do a sick man more harm than good in removing him from place to place; you fix and establish the disease by motion, as stakes sink deeper and more firmly into the earth by being moved up and down in the place where they are designed to stand.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Therefore, it is not enough to get remote from the public; 'tis not enough to shift the soil only; a man must flee from the popular conditions that have taken possession of his soul, he must sequester and come again to himself:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "We still carry our fetters along with us.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Our disease lies in the mind, which cannot escape from itself;",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "and therefore is to be called home and confined within itself: that is the true solitude, and that may be enjoyed even in populous cities and the courts of kings, though more commodiously apart.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Virtue is satisfied with herself, without discipline, without words, without effects.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "In our ordinary actions there is not one of a thousand that concerns ourselves.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000033_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000033_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Our own death does not sufficiently terrify and trouble us; let us, moreover, charge ourselves with those of our wives, children, and family: our own affairs do not afford us anxiety enough; let us undertake those of our neighbours and friends, still more to break our brains and torment us:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Solitude seems to me to wear the best favour in such as have already employed their most active and flourishing age in the world's service, after the example of Thales.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000036_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000036_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "'tis no light thing to make a sure retreat; it will be enough for us to do without mixing other enterprises.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000036_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000036_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Since God gives us leisure to order our removal, let us make ready, truss our baggage, take leave betimes of the company, and disentangle ourselves from those violent importunities that engage us elsewhere and separate us from ourselves.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "We must break the knot of our obligations, how strong soever, and hereafter love this or that, but espouse nothing but ourselves: that is to say, let the remainder be our own, but not so joined and so close as not to be forced away without flaying us or tearing out part of our whole.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000037_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000037_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "'tis time to wean ourselves from society when we can no longer add anything to it; he who is not in a condition to lend must forbid himself to borrow.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000037_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000037_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Our forces begin to fail us; let us call them in and concentrate them in and for ourselves.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000037_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000037_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Let him soothe and caress himself, and above all things be sure to govern himself with reverence to his reason and conscience to that degree as to be ashamed to make a false step in their presence:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000040_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000040_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "There are some complexions more proper for these precepts of retirement than others.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000040_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000040_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Why therefore should we, contrary to their laws, enslave our own contentment to the power of another?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "A great deal less would serve my turn well enough.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000043_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000043_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "'tis enough for me, under fortune's favour, to prepare myself for her disgrace, and, being at my ease, to represent to myself, as far as my imagination can stretch, the ill to come; as we do at jousts and tiltings, where we counterfeit war in the greatest calm of peace.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000044_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000044_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "The employment a man should choose for such a life ought neither to be a laborious nor an unpleasing one; otherwise 'tis to no purpose at all to be retired.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000044_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000044_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "And this depends upon every one's liking and humour.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000053_000000",
