        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000058_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "I for my part care for no other books, but either such as are pleasant and easy, to amuse me, or those that comfort and instruct me how to regulate my life and death:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000064_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000064_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Now, as to the end that Pliny and Cicero propose to us of glory, 'tis infinitely wide of my account.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000067_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000067_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "they have only retired to take a better leap, and by a stronger motion to give a brisker charge into the crowd.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000067_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000067_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Let the people be to you one, and be you one to the whole people.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000067_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000067_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "You are no more to concern yourself how the world talks of you, but how you are to talk to yourself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6713_56749_000067_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6713/56749/6713_56749_000067_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6713",
        "content": "Retire yourself into yourself, but first prepare yourself there to receive yourself: it were a folly to trust yourself in your own hands, if you cannot govern yourself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
